tbamud-rwb build notes: MSVC 4 (obsolete)
===========================================

This file existed in stock TbaMUD to describe compiling the C server with MSVC 4.
The Rust rewrite builds only with Cargo and targets modern Rust toolchains, so
MSVC 4 is not supported.  Build on a current operating system with:

    cargo build --release

See ../README.md and doc/porting.txt.
